image-prompt-studio-root-marker-v1
This marker identifies the Image Prompt Studio repository root.
When the app starts, it walks up from the executable looking for this file.
If found, app data is stored under <repo>/test-data/ (gitignored) so dev runs
and the locally published exe share the same state.
When this marker is absent (distributed exe), the app stores all state in
<exe-folder>/data/ if writable, otherwise %LOCALAPPDATA%/ImagePromptStudio/.
The first line above is a magic signature; do not remove it.
